1.Update a bit ( to 1 or 0)
code:
 {
   ...>
   ...>
   ...>     Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
   ...>     int n = sc.nextInt();
   ...>
   ...>     int pos =2;
   ...>     int number= 0b0101,BitMask, NotBitMask, opr;
   ...>     if (n==1) {
    ...>         BitMask = 1<<pos;                     //set operation
   ...>         opr = BitMask | number;
   ...>         System.out.print(opr);
   ...>     }
   ...>     else {
   ...>         BitMask = 1<<pos;                     //clear operation 
   ...>         NotBitMask = ~(BitMask);
   ...>         opr = NotBitMask & number;
   ...>          System.out.print(opr);
   ...>     }
   ...> }
Output :
if 1 performs set operation and for 0 performs clear operation.

2. Get Bit at a given position
Code :

 {
   ...>     Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
